### Submitting for review

If your PR meets the above requirements, select **Ready for review**, then add a reviewer: have any relevant subject matter experts (like engineers or product managers) review your work first, then add the [tech writer assigned to your specific vertical](https://confluence.braze.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=75039896). If you're not sure which tech writer to add, you can add `braze-inc/docs-team` instead.

Thanks for contributing! We look forward to reading your work.
